{"tid":818853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中電：不排除停電","createTime":"2018-09-14T11:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T12:12:38.000Z","uid":5195,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"10cce1bc8953c3838b4b3669655da7770adf1227","tid":818853,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:26:36.000Z","msg":"超強颱風「山竹」即將迫近，中電發新聞稿，指會致力維持供電系統安全運作，但惡劣天氣有機會引致電壓驟降、供電不穩或甚至停電，呼籲若市民發現戶外有電線斷落或電線杆倒塌，立刻致電中電 24 小時緊急服務熱線。<br />\n<br />\n港燈則表示，會提醒所有當值人員加強警覺，確保電力供應的穩定，並加派人手當值檢查應急設備，連日來已派人巡查供電系統，預防水浸，另外會按需要加裝防洪閘或其他防洪設施，颱風襲港期間會密切留意天氣變化。"},{"pid":"8f2ea996f8ff7b95fce35c09ab92a821357694b0","tid":818853,"uid":208726,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:32:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"437ff2933e401039f7aeccde6388f64f36bb5c70","tid":818853,"uid":6297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:35:00.000Z","msg":"使條撚驚呀！公屋大廈有後備柴油發電機房"},{"pid":"87f538fd73111d1fd901d96ba036a72e9bf5fb2b","tid":818853,"uid":48334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"437ff2933e401039f7aeccde6388f64f36bb5c70","tid":818853,"uid":6297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:35:00.000Z","msg":"使條撚驚呀！公屋大廈有後備柴油發電機房"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"俾公共空間咋"},{"pid":"a3d66a47100e0a41e6fb68b8cc78d20dfa1237d1","tid":818853,"uid":134958,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外,,<span style=\"color: red;\">打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支</span>,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n來吧~~~&nbsp;<br />\n大混亂~~~&nbsp;<br />\n特大災難~~~&nbsp;<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西Hi的日子</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f872501b917467b2ed9de77f4a102ba3410de0e8","tid":818853,"uid":120462,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"caa9ce082c8fe793d